Collections.rule:
Individual: @F*(rdf:ID=(@F*))
Types: Review
Facts: publishingDate @B* (xsd:dateTime),
       products @H* (xsd:integer),
       hours @F* (xsd:decimal),
       reviewEarlyAccess @C* (xsd:boolean),
       recommended @I* (xsd:boolean),
       text @J*,
       reviews @G* (rdf:ID)

Individual: @F*(rdf:ID=(@F*))
Types: Game
Facts: about @A*
Facts: description @B*
Facts: earlyAccess @D* (xsd:boolean)
Facts: price @I* (xsd:float)
Facts: releaseDate @J* (xsd:date)
Facts: title @L*
